## 8. What Was Not Built

| Feature | Reason |
|---|---|
| User authentication | Single-user tool. Auth adds surface area with no value. |
| Mobile native app | Web is sufficient at tablet width. A native build pipeline adds maintenance burden. |
| Social or peer features | Moderation complexity and cold start problem arrive before core value is validated. |
| Spaced repetition | Deferred to V2. Core practice loop needs validation first. |
| Resume or LinkedIn integration | Different job-to-be-done. Out of scope. |
| Percentile scoring | No comparative data pool exists. Any percentile would be fabricated. |

