## 9. Success Metrics

**North Star:** Average framework score increases by 0.5 or more points per step over four weeks of daily practice.

**Input metrics:**
- Sessions completed per week (target: 5 or more)
- Habit completion rate (target: 80% of days with at least 3 of 4 habits complete)
- Problem type coverage (target: all 7 types attempted within two weeks)

**Behavioral indicators:**
- User reaches Intermediate difficulty within two weeks
- Radar chart shape becomes more uniform over time, with no single step consistently at 1 or 2
- Daily summary is opened on 80% or more of practice days

**Guardrail metrics:**
- AI interviewer character breaks, monitored by periodic manual review of session logs
- Score inflation: if average scores trend above 4.5 without corresponding difficulty increase, the evaluator prompt is too lenient

